            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "2月社會融資增2.38萬億人幣   高於預期",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">人民銀行公布，初步統計，2026年前兩個月社會融資規模增量累計為9.6萬億元（人民幣．下同），比上年同期多3162億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">按上月公布的1月社融規模增量7.22萬億元計算，即2月社會融資規模增2.38萬億元，高於預期的2.133萬億元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15738425-2%e6%9c%88%e7%a4%be%e6%9c%83%e8%9e%8d%e8%b3%87%e5%a2%9e2-38%e8%90%ac%e5%84%84%e4%ba%ba%e5%b9%a3-%e9%ab%98%e6%96%bc%e9%a0%90%e6%9c%9f",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251021_GL_source-web_rmb_yuan.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-13 17:35:23",
